1
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:52,180
=Gorgeous Dream=
(Adapted from the novel "The Charming Evil Consort.")

2
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:55,020
=Episode 1=

3
00:00:55,720 --> 00:00:58,837
(The women of the Liu clan)
(Because the Liu clan head, Liu Qinghe embezzled tax silver.)

4
00:00:59,212 --> 00:01:00,773
(The men were exiled
to the Northern Frontier.)

5
00:01:01,333 --> 00:01:01,972
(The women)

6
00:01:02,172 --> 00:01:04,292
(were all sent into
the prisonlike Jade Spy Bureau.)

7
00:01:04,693 --> 00:01:05,893
(They endured hardship for four years.)

8
00:01:06,092 --> 00:01:07,693
(Now their suffering has finally ended.)

9
00:01:08,012 --> 00:01:09,490
(The new Emperor
has granted a general pardon.)

10
00:01:10,413 --> 00:01:12,893
(Liu clan, we have returned.)

11
00:01:16,773 --> 00:01:17,852
We are finally home.

12
00:01:19,133 --> 00:01:20,012
We have finally returned.

13
00:01:21,812 --> 00:01:22,452
This is wonderful.

14
00:01:23,693 --> 00:01:24,333
Yes.

15
00:01:26,452 --> 00:01:28,693
Sprinkle water to sweep away misfortune.

16
00:01:29,852 --> 00:01:32,253
Step over fire to welcome good fortune.

17
00:01:35,537 --> 00:01:37,437
(Prefectural Judge of Ning City,
Liu Qinghe)

18
00:01:38,493 --> 00:01:38,893
Father.

19
00:01:38,973 --> 00:01:39,732
(The Dowager of the Liu Clan)
The children are here.

20
00:01:39,773 --> 00:01:40,693
(Ancestral Matriarch)
They have all arrived.

21
00:01:41,133 --> 00:01:41,613
Mother.

22
00:01:42,333 --> 00:01:43,533
Welcome home, everyone.

23
00:01:44,893 --> 00:01:46,893
The battle dance strengthens the spirit.

24
00:01:47,493 --> 00:01:50,012
Good fortune will never leave us.

25
00:01:57,133 --> 00:01:57,693
Good.

26
00:01:58,525 --> 00:01:59,387
(The adopted daughter
of the Liu Residence, Shen Wanqing.)

27
00:01:59,413 --> 00:02:00,092
Mother.

28
00:02:00,773 --> 00:02:01,893
Who are the people inside?

29
00:02:07,092 --> 00:02:07,613
Look,

30
00:02:08,372 --> 00:02:09,493
they dance so well.

31
00:02:15,173 --> 00:02:15,573
Brother.

32
00:02:15,613 --> 00:02:17,692
Mother, you have finally come home.

33
00:02:18,252 --> 00:02:19,900
You have lived
under the Liu clan's roof for years.

34
00:02:20,013 --> 00:02:21,293
You have enjoyed comfort and abundance.

35
00:02:21,412 --> 00:02:23,372
The Liu clan has treated you
as if you were their own.

36
00:02:23,372 --> 00:02:26,893
Now it is time for you
to repay the kindness that raised you.

37
00:02:28,053 --> 00:02:28,773
So

38
00:02:30,092 --> 00:02:32,053
you should set out
on your final journey in peace.

39
00:02:36,925 --> 00:02:37,444
This...

40
00:02:37,444 --> 00:02:39,324
Brother, what do you mean?

41
00:02:51,853 --> 00:02:53,212
You have spent four years in prison.

42
00:02:53,333 --> 00:02:54,490
You have already lost your good name.

43
00:02:55,532 --> 00:02:56,252
The Liu clan

44
00:02:57,293 --> 00:02:58,733
will no longer allow you to remain.

45
00:02:59,532 --> 00:03:01,453
Our reputation
is no longer what it once was.

46
00:03:01,733 --> 00:03:03,652
Your deaths
are needed to prove our loyalty.

47
00:03:04,173 --> 00:03:06,372
If you willingly die
in the name of chastity,

48
00:03:06,453 --> 00:03:08,812
you may still win
the new Emperor's favor.

49
00:03:09,453 --> 00:03:10,053
Such a choice

50
00:03:11,493 --> 00:03:12,893
will be considered a worthy death.

51
00:03:19,932 --> 00:03:20,532
Do it.

52
00:03:23,053 --> 00:03:23,932
Mother, go!

53
00:03:25,252 --> 00:03:25,692
This way!

54
00:03:28,372 --> 00:03:28,812
Hurry!

55
00:03:28,893 --> 00:03:29,652
Husband, no!

56
00:03:29,932 --> 00:03:31,132
No! Stop!

57
00:03:31,853 --> 00:03:32,293
Come here!

58
00:03:32,613 --> 00:03:33,493
Help!

59
00:03:34,812 --> 00:03:35,333
Come here!

60
00:03:37,893 --> 00:03:40,453
(The son of Liu Qinghe, Liu Wenyu)
Wenyu, it's me, Xiaohua! Spare me!

61
00:03:40,853 --> 00:03:41,733
Enough.

62
00:03:42,453 --> 00:03:43,293
(The second brother of Liu Qinghe, Liu Qingming)
I am sorry.

63
00:03:43,692 --> 00:03:45,453
This is the rule of the Liu clan.

64
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:46,462
(The younger brother of Xie Ruilan,
Xie Yaozu)

65
00:03:46,493 --> 00:03:46,972
Young master.

66
00:03:46,972 --> 00:03:47,733
Do not blame me.

67
00:03:48,053 --> 00:03:49,333
This is your fate.

68
00:03:51,092 --> 00:03:51,692
Let go!

69
00:03:53,372 --> 00:03:54,252
Everyone, let go!

70
00:03:54,412 --> 00:03:54,932
All of you, let go!

71
00:03:58,372 --> 00:03:58,932
Release!

72
00:04:00,773 --> 00:04:01,252
Release!

73
00:04:02,812 --> 00:04:03,453
Let go!

74
00:04:10,053 --> 00:04:10,692
Brother.

75
00:04:14,453 --> 00:04:16,093
Because you embezzled silver,

76
00:04:16,332 --> 00:04:18,252
we took the blame for the Liu clan.

77
00:04:19,452 --> 00:04:20,132
Why?

78
00:04:21,653 --> 00:04:23,452
Why should we be the ones who must die?

79
00:04:24,053 --> 00:04:25,053
In the Jade Spy Bureau,

80
00:04:25,332 --> 00:04:27,213
it was we who endured every torment.

81
00:04:27,812 --> 00:04:28,692
- Why?
- Wanqing!

82
00:04:28,790 --> 00:04:29,132
Wanqing!

83
00:04:29,132 --> 00:04:30,213
You are the ones who should die!

84
00:04:30,692 --> 00:04:31,413
It is you!

85
00:04:32,012 --> 00:04:32,452
Move!

86
00:04:35,093 --> 00:04:35,932
Have them open the door!

87
00:04:36,692 --> 00:04:37,853
Have them open the door!

88
00:04:38,613 --> 00:04:39,132
Say it!

89
00:04:39,653 --> 00:04:40,493
Open the door!

90
00:04:50,413 --> 00:04:51,173
Mother.

91
00:04:52,293 --> 00:04:54,493
I will never allow anyone to tarnish

92
00:04:54,772 --> 00:04:56,332
the good name of the Liu clan.

93
00:04:56,653 --> 00:04:57,372
Mother.

94
00:05:00,452 --> 00:05:01,252
Mother.

95
00:05:02,293 --> 00:05:03,892
Why will you not listen to my son?

96
00:05:04,252 --> 00:05:05,572
Listen to my son!

97
00:05:23,572 --> 00:05:24,132
No!

98
00:05:24,132 --> 00:05:25,332
My son, Qinghe

99
00:05:25,533 --> 00:05:27,692
has struggled bitterly
to reach this day.

100
00:05:27,692 --> 00:05:28,772
Your sacrifice

101
00:05:29,093 --> 00:05:31,332
will become
the foundation of the Liu clan.

102
00:05:33,093 --> 00:05:34,613
To die for the family

103
00:05:34,853 --> 00:05:37,293
is the highest honor for us women.

104
00:05:39,173 --> 00:05:40,293
My son is right.

105
00:05:40,932 --> 00:05:42,252
From this day on,

106
00:05:42,533 --> 00:05:44,613
our names will be written separately
in the family registry.

107
00:05:45,692 --> 00:05:47,572
The ancestral hall will bear our names.

108
00:05:48,173 --> 00:05:49,213
Our fathers and brothers,

109
00:05:49,653 --> 00:05:50,332
our husbands,

110
00:05:50,692 --> 00:05:51,372
our children,

111
00:05:51,572 --> 00:05:52,252
and our families

112
00:05:53,132 --> 00:05:54,733
will all be proud of us.

113
00:05:55,213 --> 00:05:57,533
The Ancestress has acted
with great righteousness.

114
00:05:58,973 --> 00:06:01,452
The Ancestress has acted
with great righteousness.

115
00:06:02,252 --> 00:06:05,853
We respectfully send
the Ancestress on her final journey.

116
00:06:06,932 --> 00:06:09,452
We respectfully send
the Ancestress on her final journey.

117
00:06:09,452 --> 00:06:10,613
My son...

118
00:06:11,812 --> 00:06:12,533
From this day forward,

119
00:06:13,932 --> 00:06:14,932
Liu clan

120
00:06:15,733 --> 00:06:17,012
will be entrusted to you.

121
00:07:00,053 --> 00:07:01,572
We spent a great deal to bring you here.

122
00:07:02,692 --> 00:07:04,653
You must handle everything perfectly.

123
00:07:04,812 --> 00:07:05,332
Sister.

124
00:07:05,613 --> 00:07:07,613
(The matriarch of the Liu clan, Xie Ruilan)
No one must notice anything amiss.

125
00:07:08,493 --> 00:07:09,053
Rest assured.

126
00:07:09,452 --> 00:07:11,692
I promise I will take care
of everything flawlessly.

127
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:12,932
Even if the authorities investigate,

128
00:07:13,252 --> 00:07:15,173
they will find nothing
but a case of self-immolation.

129
00:07:20,572 --> 00:07:21,653
Shen Wanqing.

130
00:07:22,372 --> 00:07:24,132
You are no adopted daughter
of the Liu Residence.

131
00:07:24,493 --> 00:07:25,733
You were nothing more than

132
00:07:25,892 --> 00:07:27,413
an orphan we seized for ourselves.

133
00:07:28,293 --> 00:07:29,692
Through your deaths,

134
00:07:30,332 --> 00:07:32,093
the chastity memorial we earn

135
00:07:32,093 --> 00:07:33,692
can exempt us from three years of tax.

136
00:07:33,892 --> 00:07:35,493
It can be exchanged
for ten thousand taels.

137
00:07:36,173 --> 00:07:37,613
Do not blame me.

138
00:07:38,372 --> 00:07:39,213
If you must blame someone,

139
00:07:39,332 --> 00:07:41,293
blame this cruel world
that devours people.

140
00:07:42,012 --> 00:07:43,812
Your identity as the last orphan
of the Shen family

141
00:07:45,093 --> 00:07:46,293
from this moment on

142
00:07:47,413 --> 00:07:48,853
will forever remain a secret.

143
00:07:52,493 --> 00:07:54,973
To die under the name
of The Seven Martyr Heroines

144
00:07:55,293 --> 00:07:57,493
is the finest end you could hope for.

145
00:07:58,973 --> 00:08:00,293
Your name will be remembered.

146
00:08:01,572 --> 00:08:03,053
The world will speak of you.

147
00:08:03,892 --> 00:08:04,772
You need not thank me.

148
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:47,132
(The spirit tablets of Martyr Liu Wangshu,
Martyr Li Shushen, and Martyr Liu Mingzhen)

149
00:09:47,132 --> 00:09:48,412
(Just as Liu Qinghe wished.)

150
00:09:48,813 --> 00:09:51,252
(The spirit tablet of Martyr Shen Wanqing)
(The Emperor honors the sacrifice of The Seven Martyr Heroines.)

151
00:09:51,453 --> 00:09:52,372
(A Household of Chastity)
(The Liu clan is greatly rewarded.)

152
00:09:52,933 --> 00:09:54,453
(A gilded plaque
proclaiming their purity)

153
00:09:54,573 --> 00:09:55,412
(is hung high.)

154
00:09:55,892 --> 00:09:56,892
(And Liu Qinghe)

155
00:09:57,892 --> 00:10:00,213
(is promoted
to Prefectural Judge of Ning City.)

156
00:10:01,493 --> 00:10:02,012
(Mother.)

157
00:10:02,813 --> 00:10:03,412
(Wanqing.)

158
00:10:03,733 --> 00:10:05,772
(A Household of Chastity)
(Your sacrifices were worth it.)

159
00:10:16,493 --> 00:10:17,853
(You now wear a new face.)

160
00:10:18,933 --> 00:10:20,733
(From this moment on,
Shen Wanqing no longer exists.)

161
00:10:22,292 --> 00:10:23,333
(The Liu clan's blood feud)

162
00:10:24,453 --> 00:10:25,693
(do you still intend to avenge it?)

163
00:10:26,693 --> 00:10:27,973
(This new face)

164
00:10:28,693 --> 00:10:29,412
(is gentle,)

165
00:10:30,493 --> 00:10:31,132
(obedient,)

166
00:10:32,412 --> 00:10:33,613
(and harmless.)

167
00:10:34,093 --> 00:10:36,493
(It is exactly the type
those bandits favor most.)

168
00:10:36,733 --> 00:10:38,853
(As long as the lie of the Liu clan's
martyrdom remains unbroken,)

169
00:10:38,933 --> 00:10:39,933
(those orphaned girls)

170
00:10:40,132 --> 00:10:41,733
(will forever be recorded
in their ledgers)

171
00:10:41,733 --> 00:10:42,813
(as wrongful sacrifices.)

172
00:10:43,052 --> 00:10:45,333
(Happiness)
(I will appear before each of them)

173
00:10:45,372 --> 00:10:47,493
(in the very form they adored)

174
00:10:47,652 --> 00:10:48,973
(at their funerals.)

175
00:10:48,973 --> 00:10:50,162
(Three years later, Ning City)

176
00:10:50,737 --> 00:10:52,425
(Happiness)

177
00:10:52,762 --> 00:10:54,573
(The son of Liu Qinghe, Liu Wenyu.)

178
00:10:54,573 --> 00:10:55,933
The auspicious hour has arrived.

179
00:10:56,172 --> 00:10:58,093
The bride enters the residence.

180
00:10:59,252 --> 00:11:02,052
(Happiness)
First, sprinkle pomelo water to purify all defilement.

181
00:11:02,813 --> 00:11:05,892
Second, step over the fire basin
to welcome good fortune.

182
00:11:06,693 --> 00:11:10,372
May the household prosper
and enjoy a hundred years of peace.

183
00:11:10,892 --> 00:11:12,172
The bride looks unfamiliar.

184
00:11:12,190 --> 00:11:13,172
She must be from another town.

185
00:11:13,573 --> 00:11:14,652
I heard that this bride,

186
00:11:14,853 --> 00:11:16,252
though merely the daughter
of a merchant,

187
00:11:16,613 --> 00:11:19,093
(Huan Xi, maid of Lan Mengyan)
comes from the wealthiest family in Yang City.

188
00:11:19,453 --> 00:11:20,333
Look at her dowry.

189
00:11:20,613 --> 00:11:21,933
Who here could compare?

190
00:11:22,733 --> 00:11:24,172
What good is being wealthy?

191
00:11:24,493 --> 00:11:26,412
She is still a parentless orphan.

192
00:11:26,613 --> 00:11:28,693
Once she enters the Liu Residence,
her days may not be easy.

193
00:11:30,675 --> 00:11:32,875
(The younger brother of Xie Ruilan,
Xie Yaozu.)

194
00:11:32,875 --> 00:11:34,862
(Happiness)

195
00:11:36,772 --> 00:11:37,372
Qing.

196
00:11:38,252 --> 00:11:38,772
We are home.

197
00:11:41,292 --> 00:11:41,892
Do not be shy.

198
00:11:42,412 --> 00:11:43,453
Let me introduce my family to you.

199
00:11:49,252 --> 00:11:50,772
Mother, this is Lan Mengyan.

200
00:11:54,892 --> 00:11:55,973
The dowry is complete, Sister.

201
00:12:05,012 --> 00:12:06,093
Excellent.

202
00:12:06,532 --> 00:12:07,532
Excellent.

203
00:12:22,412 --> 00:12:23,213
(The Liu clan,)

204
00:12:24,772 --> 00:12:25,853
(I have returned.)
